                <p>Users are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their login credentials and for all activities that occur under their account. You agree to use TrackIT only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these terms. You may not use the service to distribute malicious content, harass others, or interfere with system functionality. TrackIT reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these conditions without prior notice.</p>
                <p>All content you create or upload to TrackIT (including tasks, notes and attachments) remains your property. However, by using the platform, you grant TrackIT a limited license to host, display, and process your content for the sole purpose of delivering the services. You are responsible for ensuring that any content you share does not infringe upon the rights of others.</p>
                <p>TWe take reasonable measures to secure your data and provide backup systems. However, TrackIT is not liable for any data loss, corruption, or system failure beyond our control. Users are encouraged to export important data regularly using the built-in export features.</p>
